613
00:52:46,378 --> 00:52:49,181
They put me on the night shift.
- I think he did something terrible.

614
00:52:49,206 --> 00:52:51,264
They say that I'm being rewarded.

615
00:52:51,289 --> 00:52:54,545
Well.. If you guys ever want a tour
of the neighbourhood...

616
