Oh..ehe..
I'm sorry.

625
00:59:53,510 --> 00:59:54,393
Thank you.

626
00:59:57,013 --> 00:59:58,666
Thank you for meeting with me.

627
00:59:58,958 --> 00:59:59,964
It's fine.

628
01:00:00,239 --> 01:00:02,357
I was a little surprised
to hear from you though.

629
01:00:02,618 --> 01:00:03,759
Last time we spoke...

630
01:00:03,784 --> 01:00:05,579
I said I didn't want to know any more.

631
01:00:06,530 --> 01:00:09,482
Having Ehh..
Had a little distance I Ehm...

632
01:00:11,059 --> 01:00:13,715
Well, I.. I realize I could use
some.. some closure.

633
01:00:13,918 --> 01:00:16,739
I mean there.. there's just
to many unanswered questions.

634
01:00:16,986 --> 01:00:18,243
I understand.

635
01:00:19,274 --> 01:00:21,618
I brought what I have on the Higgins case.

636
01:00:27,134 --> 01:00:28,845
That's Annabelle there.

637
01:00:29,228 --> 01:00:30,712
The Higgins girl.

638
01:00:31,503 --> 01:00:33,597
That was clearly taken before she

639
01:00:33,622 --> 01:00:35,162
got caught up in the cult.

640
01:00:36,764 --> 01:00:39,943
Looks a lot different than the last time
you saw her, doesn't she?

641
01:00:43,900 --> 01:00:46,221
This cult that she was in.

642
01:00:46,697 --> 01:00:48,837
Did you look further into it?

643
01:00:49,143 --> 01:00:51,002
For what, specifically?

644
01:00:51,027 --> 01:00:53,237
I don't know.
There must have been some motive

645
01:00:53,262 --> 01:00:54,808
for their attacks.

646
01:00:55,366 --> 01:00:57,429
Crazy people do crazy things.

647
01:00:57,454 --> 01:00:58,804
...crazy things.
I know.

648
01:00:59,881 --> 01:01:01,904
They didn't think they were crazy.

649
01:01:02,959 --> 01:01:04,936
They have to have had a reason.

650
01:01:06,444 --> 01:01:08,082
After a little more digging...

651
01:01:08,380 --> 01:01:10,879
I did find that their act
was in devotional.

652
01:01:11,181 --> 01:01:12,496
That they were...

653
01:01:12,942 --> 01:01:16,212
They were actually trying
to conjure something up.

654
01:01:18,576 --> 01:01:19,820
Like.. Like what?

655
01:01:19,845 --> 01:01:21,873
The Devil.. Demons...

656
01:01:22,299 --> 01:01:24,830
The Tooth-fairy, I don't know specifically.

657
01:01:25,183 --> 01:01:27,214
It doesn't really matter any..
- Why not?

658
01:01:28,217 --> 01:01:31,037
Well, because this is all
just a bunch of hocus pocus.

659
01:01:31,225 --> 01:01:32,303
Ahm...

660
01:01:33,850 --> 01:01:35,123
Please.

661
01:01:44,843 --> 01:01:45,859
Ma'am.

662
01:01:47,406 --> 01:01:48,922
These were miscreants.

663
01:01:49,859 --> 01:01:52,468
They were probably hopped up
on god knows what.

664
01:01:52,705 --> 01:01:54,003
And it made 'em...

665
01:01:54,028 --> 01:01:55,956
see and do
all sorts of...

666
01:01:57,130 --> 01:01:58,791
terrible things.

667
01:02:08,195 --> 01:02:10,508
Does this mean anything to you?

668
01:02:14,452 --> 01:02:16,335
Have you ever heard the expression...

669
01:02:16,724 --> 01:02:19,135
"sometimes a cigar is just a cigar"?

670
01:02:19,256 --> 01:02:21,881
Then you won't mind if I eh.. keep this...

671
01:02:22,640 --> 01:02:24,540
one for myself?

