01:03:06,036 --> 01:03:07,558
just browsing really.

680
01:03:08,447 --> 01:03:10,268
I just learned something.

681
01:03:11,095 --> 01:03:12,962
You're a terrible liar.

682
01:03:15,600 --> 01:03:17,342
What is it you're looking for?

683
01:03:19,294 --> 01:03:21,357
Maybe I'll come back.
- Mia!

684
01:03:21,856 --> 01:03:22,981
I'm old.

685
01:03:23,262 --> 01:03:26,317
Which means that there's very little
that surprises me anymore.

686
01:03:26,521 --> 01:03:29,319
And if it does, I'm too tired to show it.

687
01:03:30,051 --> 01:03:32,122
Now. Are you gonna tell me?
Or are we just...

688
01:03:32,147 --> 01:03:35,205
I think my family
is being haunted by a.. a ghost.

689
01:03:37,030 --> 01:03:39,389
Isle four. Follow me.

690
01:03:44,780 --> 01:03:46,287
I.. I know it sounds crazy.

691
01:03:46,312 --> 01:03:49,108
The ghost of this girl haunting us.
But I.. I just...

692
01:03:49,133 --> 01:03:51,493
No crazier than the red sea parting.

693
01:03:51,891 --> 01:03:54,130
To non-believers it's all crazy.

694
01:03:54,535 --> 01:03:56,480
Do you believe in this stuff?

695
01:03:57,435 --> 01:03:59,331
Let's just say that...

696
01:03:59,356 --> 01:04:02,339
I've had one or two experiences
in my life that eh...

697
01:04:03,128 --> 01:04:05,456
helped me to keep an open mind.

698
01:04:13,489 --> 01:04:17,685
