are experiencing is the ghost of that girl.

699
01:04:18,584 --> 01:04:19,607
Why not?

700
01:04:19,632 --> 01:04:22,367
Well, ghosts haunts specific places.

701
01:04:22,696 --> 01:04:25,594
Usually where something terrible
has happened.

702
01:04:25,619 --> 01:04:27,407
Like your old house.

703
01:04:28,160 --> 01:04:31,067
We.. We moved and it's still happening.

704
01:04:31,092 --> 01:04:33,098
Which is why I don't think it's a ghost.

705
01:04:33,807 --> 01:04:35,830
But now, that cult...

706
01:04:35,855 --> 01:04:38,573
You said that they were trying
to summon something?

707
01:04:39,679 --> 01:04:41,429
From what I've read in the past...

708
01:04:42,117 --> 01:04:44,648
These cults, they don't summon ghosts.

709
01:04:45,821 --> 01:04:48,657
They summon inhuman spirits.

710
01:04:48,775 --> 01:04:51,266
Something that has never
existed in the flesh.

711
01:04:52,784 --> 01:04:54,128
Demons?

712
01:04:55,268 --> 01:04:56,987
What.. What do they want?

713
01:04:58,212 --> 01:04:59,306
A soul.

714
01:05:00,586 --> 01:05:03,406
And they won't stop until they get one.

715
01:05:05,053 --> 01:05:06,772
What do I.. What do I do?

716
01:05:08,234 --> 01:05:11,070
Hopefully the answer
is in one of these books.

717
01:05:27,557 --> 01:05:29,713
My daughter, Ruby.

718
01:05:31,060 --> 01:05:34,060
She passed away
when she was about your age.

719
01:05:35,944 --> 01:05:37,092
I'm sorry.

720
01:05:39,024 --> 01:05:42,860
Without her I felt like
I had nothing else to live for so...

721
01:05:44,404 --> 01:05:47,928
But as I lay there,
waiting for it all to end...

722
01:05:49,929 --> 01:05:51,265
I heard her voice.

723
01:05:53,515 --> 01:05:55,792
She told me that it wasn't my time.

724
01:05:56,712 --> 01:05:59,173
That God had another purpose for me.

725
01:06:00,525 --> 01:06:02,619
You too have a purpose Mia.

726
01:06:03,506 --> 01:06:05,725
To protect your family.

727
01:06:05,998 --> 01:06:08,694
So don't think you're crazy
for trying to do that.

728
01:06:08,718 --> 01:06:10,992
You do what you think is right.

729
01:06:12,183 --> 01:06:14,492
You do what you have to do.

730
01:07:05,417 --> 01:07:07,713
The Devil prays on the weak

731
01:07:07,738 --> 01:07:09,662
and the vulnerable.

732
01:07:16,490 --> 01:07:19,037
Seeking to devour their souls.

733
01:07:20,067 --> 01:07:21,567
To perform...

734
01:07:21,988 --> 01:07:23,176
Incantations...

735
01:07:25,104 --> 01:07:27,643
Spilling the blood of kin.

736
01:07:29,277 --> 01:07:31,474
Spilling the blood of the innocent.

737
01:07:39,275 --> 01:07:41,431
How do I stop it?

738
01:07:50,111 --> 01:07:51,224
