can always be placed.

774
01:12:39,031 --> 01:12:40,608
What do we do in the meantime?

775
01:12:41,839 --> 01:12:44,526
I can't have Leah anywhere near that doll.

776
01:12:47,065 --> 01:12:48,745
Let me take her.

777
01:12:49,618 --> 01:12:53,298
Perhaps if she's stored in a sacred place
it will weaken the demon enough.

778
01:12:53,323 --> 01:12:55,596
