779
01:12:58,315 --> 01:12:59,838
Thank you Father.

780
01:13:00,436 --> 01:13:01,952
Of course.

781
01:13:58,515 --> 01:13:59,693
Come on.

782
01:13:59,718 --> 01:14:01,257
