Doctors orders.

783
01:14:01,282 --> 01:14:03,005
Oh, no no John.
I can't.

784
01:14:03,030 --> 01:14:04,411
Not until I know it's not coming back.

785
01:14:04,436 --> 01:14:07,275
Mia. Come on.
What if.. what if...

786
01:14:07,300 --> 01:14:09,986
John. I can't.
- What if I just stayed up with her?

787
01:14:10,011 --> 01:14:11,479
You get some rest.

788
01:14:13,012 --> 01:14:14,036
Alright?

789
01:14:14,061 --> 01:14:15,239
Okay.

790
01:14:15,934 --> 01:14:17,012
Good night.

791
01:14:17,468 --> 01:14:18,538
John.

792
01:14:21,434 --> 01:14:22,489
Yeah.

793
01:14:23,066 --> 01:14:25,449
Thank you for believing me.

794
01:14:25,725 --> 01:14:28,241
I didn't know if.. if you would.

795
01:14:28,639 --> 01:14:29,819
Mia!

796
01:14:30,343 --> 01:14:31,202
